OL,3,CMan charged after 87-year-old
OL,4,Callegedly attacked and kidnapped
OL,6,FA man has been charged after an 87-
OL,7,Fyear-old pensioner was allegedly
OL,8,Fforced into a car, attacked, and
OL,9,Fthrown out on a dark road 15 miles
OL,10,Faway.
OL,12,FShohad Miah, of Firbank Road, Royton,
OL,13,Fhas been charged with kidnap, section
OL,14,F18 with intent to cause grievous
OL,15,Fbodily harm, robbery and intentional
OL,16,Fstrangulation.
