OL,3,CMan charged after 87-year-old
OL,4,Callegedly attacked and kidnapped
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said the
OL,7,Fpensioner was reportedly walking home
OL,8,Fat 9pm on 15 September on Lee Street,
OL,9,FOldham, when he was forced into a
OL,10,Fblack car, while demands were made for
OL,11,Fhis money and personal items.
OL,13,FHe was attacked and eventually pushed
OL,14,Fout of the car on a dark road in the
OL,15,FRishworth area of West Yorkshire,
OL,16,Fofficers said.
OL,18,FThe elderly man eventually found help
OL,19,Fby knocking on a door at around
OL,20,F10:40pm, they added.
