OL,4,Callegedly attacked and kidnapped
OL,6,FMr Miah has been remanded into custody
OL,7,Fand will appear at Tameside
OL,8,FMagistrates Court on Tuesday, 24
OL,9,FSeptember.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police said:
OL,12,F"Officers are appealing to the public
OL,13,Ffor information to support their
OL,14,Finvestigations into this shocking
OL,15,Fincident."
OL,17,FThey added that detectives believe it
OL,18,Fwas an "isolated incident with no
OL,19,Fwider threat to the public".
